title.narrative: Innovative Farm Systems and Capabilty for Agribusiness (IFSCA)

description.narrative: The Innovative Farm Systems and Capability for Agribusiness (IFSCA) activity creates economic opportunities for sustainable farming in Nusa Tenggara Barat, Indonesia through enhanced connections in three sectors (maize, beef and vegetables), benefiting farmers, processors, and traders - including corn wholesalers, local hotels, and cattle traders.
